<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-font name="DM Sans" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"></mj-font>
    <mj-attributes>
      <mj-text font-family="'DM Sans', Calibri, Arial, sans-serif" />
      <mj-section padding="0px" />
      <mj-all font-family="'DM Sans', Calibri, Arial, sans-serif" />
    </mj-attributes>
    <mj-style>
      p { margin: 0 !important; }
      @font-face {
        font-family: 'DM Sans';
        mso-font-alt: 'Calibri';
      }
      .tag { display: inline-block; padding: 3px 12px; border-radius: 99px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; }
      .tag-cloud { background-color: #dbeafe; color: #1e40af; }
      .tag-cyber { background-color: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }
      .tag-data { background-color: #d1fae5; color: #065f46; }
      .tag-green { background-color: #fef9c3; color: #854d0e; }
      .tag-services { background-color: #ede9fe; color: #5b21b6; }
      .divider-gold { border-color: #D4952A !important; }
    </mj-style>
    <mj-preview>5 acquisitions IT Services — France &amp; Suisse — mars 2026</mj-preview>
  </mj-head>

  <mj-body width="600px">

    <!-- ====== HEADER ====== -->
    <mj-section padding="32px 40px 24px">
      <mj-column width="55%" vertical-align="middle" padding="0">
        <mj-text font-size="26px" font-weight="700" color="#1a2332" line-height="32px" padding="0px">
          Digest M&amp;A
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-size="15px" font-weight="400" color="#64748b" line-height="22px" padding="4px 0 0 0">
          IT Services · France &amp; Suisse
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-size="12px" color="#94a3b8" padding="6px 0 0 0" line-height="18px">
          Mars 2026 · 5 opérations identifiées
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="45%" vertical-align="middle" padding="0">
        <mj-image width="160px" alt="Auraïa Capital Advisory" align="right" padding="0px"
          src="data:image/png;base64," />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Gold accent line -->
    <mj-section padding="0 40px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-divider border-color="#D4952A" border-width="3px" padding="0" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- ====== STATS BAR ====== -->
    <mj-section padding="20px 0">
      <mj-column width="33.33%" padding="0 12px">
        <mj-text align="center" font-size="26px" font-weight="700" color="#D4952A" line-height="30px" padding="0px">5</mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" font-size="10px" font-weight="600" color="#94a3b8" text-transform="uppercase" letter-spacing="0.5px" padding="4px 0 0 0">Opérations</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="33.33%" padding="0 12px">
        <mj-text align="center" font-size="26px" font-weight="700" color="#D4952A" line-height="30px" padding="0px">€325M+</mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" font-size="10px" font-weight="600" color="#94a3b8" text-transform="uppercase" letter-spacing="0.5px" padding="4px 0 0 0">Valeur cumulée</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
      <mj-column width="33.33%" padding="0 12px">
        <mj-text align="center" font-size="26px" font-weight="700" color="#D4952A" line-height="30px" padding="0px">2</mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center" font-size="10px" font-weight="600" color="#94a3b8" text-transform="uppercase" letter-spacing="0.5px" padding="4px 0 0 0">Cross-border</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Thin separator -->
    <mj-section padding="0 40px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-divider border-color="#e2e8f0" border-width="1px" padding="0" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- ====== SYNTHÈSE ====== -->
    <mj-section padding="24px 40px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="11px" font-weight="700" color="#D4952A" letter-spacing="1.5px" text-transform="uppercase" padding="0px">
          Synthèse
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="10px" />
        <mj-text font-size="14px" color="#374151" line-height="24px" padding="0px">
          Le mois de mars 2026 a été marqué par une activité M&amp;A soutenue dans le secteur des services IT en France et en Suisse. La tendance dominante reste la <strong>consolidation des ESN de taille moyenne</strong> par les grands groupes, avec un accent particulier sur les compétences cloud et cybersécurité. Deux opérations cross-border franco-suisses illustrent l'intégration croissante du marché IT lémanique.
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Gold accent line -->
    <mj-section padding="0 40px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-divider border-color="#D4952A" border-width="2px" padding="0" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- ====== DEAL 1 — Highlight ====== -->
    <mj-section padding="24px 40px" border-left="4px solid #D4952A">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="10px" font-weight="700" color="#D4952A" letter-spacing="1px" text-transform="uppercase" padding="0px">
          ★ Opération majeure
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="8px" />
        <mj-text font-size="18px" font-weight="700" color="#111827" line-height="26px" padding="0px">
          Accenture → GreenIT Solutions
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="6px" />
        <mj-text font-size="12px" color="#6b7280" line-height="20px" padding="0px">
          Annoncé le 5 mars 2026 · France · VE est. <strong style="color: #D4952A;">€120M</strong> · <span class="tag tag-green">IT for Sustainability</span>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="10px" />
        <mj-text font-size="13px" color="#374151" line-height="22px" padding="0px">
          Accenture acquiert GreenIT Solutions, cabinet parisien de 200 consultants spécialisé dans l'accompagnement des entreprises vers un IT durable (Green IT, optimisation énergétique des datacenters, éco-conception logicielle). Cette acquisition illustre la montée en puissance du créneau sustainability dans les services IT. GreenIT compte parmi ses clients plusieurs entreprises du CAC 40.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="8px" />
        <mj-text font-size="11px" padding="0px">
          <a href="https://example.com/accenture-greenit" style="color: #6b7280; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db; padding-bottom: 1px;">Source ↗</a>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Deal divider -->
    <mj-section padding="0 40px">
      <mj-column><mj-divider border-color="#e2e8f0" border-width="1px" padding="0" /></mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- ====== DEAL 2 ====== -->
    <mj-section padding="24px 40px" border-left="4px solid #e2e8f0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="16px" font-weight="700" color="#111827" line-height="24px" padding="0px">
          Capgemini → CloudNow SA
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="6px" />
        <mj-text font-size="12px" color="#6b7280" line-height="20px" padding="0px">
          Annoncé le 22 mars 2026 · Suisse · VE est. <strong style="color: #D4952A;">€85M</strong> · <span class="tag tag-cloud">Cloud &amp; Infra</span>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="10px" />
        <mj-text font-size="13px" color="#374151" line-height="22px" padding="0px">
          Capgemini acquiert CloudNow SA, ESN genevoise de 320 collaborateurs spécialisée dans la migration cloud et les infrastructures hybrides. Cette acquisition renforce la présence de Capgemini en Suisse romande. Le montant de €85M valorise CloudNow à environ 2x son chiffre d'affaires.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="8px" />
        <mj-text font-size="11px" padding="0px">
          <a href="https://example.com/capgemini-cloudnow" style="color: #6b7280; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db; padding-bottom: 1px;">Source ↗</a>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Deal divider -->
    <mj-section padding="0 40px">
      <mj-column><mj-divider border-color="#e2e8f0" border-width="1px" padding="0" /></mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- ====== DEAL 3 ====== -->
    <mj-section padding="24px 40px" border-left="4px solid #e2e8f0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="16px" font-weight="700" color="#111827" line-height="24px" padding="0px">
          Sopra Steria → CyberShield France
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="6px" />
        <mj-text font-size="12px" color="#6b7280" line-height="20px" padding="0px">
          Annoncé le 18 mars 2026 · France · Montant non divulgué · <span class="tag tag-cyber">Cybersécurité</span>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="10px" />
        <mj-text font-size="13px" color="#374151" line-height="22px" padding="0px">
          Sopra Steria poursuit sa stratégie de build-up en cybersécurité avec l'acquisition de CyberShield France, pure player lyonnais d'une centaine de consultants. L'opération s'inscrit dans le plan stratégique 2025-2028 visant à faire de la cybersécurité le premier relais de croissance du groupe.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="8px" />
        <mj-text font-size="11px" padding="0px">
          <a href="https://example.com/sopra-cybershield" style="color: #6b7280; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db; padding-bottom: 1px;">Source ↗</a>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Deal divider -->
    <mj-section padding="0 40px">
      <mj-column><mj-divider border-color="#e2e8f0" border-width="1px" padding="0" /></mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- ====== DEAL 4 ====== -->
    <mj-section padding="24px 40px" border-left="4px solid #e2e8f0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="16px" font-weight="700" color="#111827" line-height="24px" padding="0px">
          Devoteam → SwissData GmbH
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="6px" />
        <mj-text font-size="12px" color="#6b7280" line-height="20px" padding="0px">
          Annoncé le 12 mars 2026 · Suisse · VE est. <strong style="color: #D4952A;">€35M</strong> · <span class="tag tag-data">Data &amp; Analytics</span>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="10px" />
        <mj-text font-size="13px" color="#374151" line-height="22px" padding="0px">
          Devoteam fait son entrée sur le marché suisse alémanique en rachetant SwissData GmbH, société zurichoise de 85 collaborateurs positionnée sur le data engineering. Cette opération permet à Devoteam d'accéder au marché germanophone et de compléter son maillage européen.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="8px" />
        <mj-text font-size="11px" padding="0px">
          <a href="https://example.com/devoteam-swissdata" style="color: #6b7280; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db; padding-bottom: 1px;">Source ↗</a>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- Deal divider -->
    <mj-section padding="0 40px">
      <mj-column><mj-divider border-color="#e2e8f0" border-width="1px" padding="0" /></mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- ====== DEAL 5 ====== -->
    <mj-section padding="24px 40px" border-left="4px solid #e2e8f0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="16px" font-weight="700" color="#111827" line-height="24px" padding="0px">
          Groupe Informatique Romand → NetPlus Sàrl
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="6px" />
        <mj-text font-size="12px" color="#6b7280" line-height="20px" padding="0px">
          Annoncé le 1 mars 2026 · Suisse · Montant non divulgué · <span class="tag tag-services">Services managés</span>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="10px" />
        <mj-text font-size="13px" color="#374151" line-height="22px" padding="0px">
          Opération entre deux acteurs locaux : le Groupe Informatique Romand (GIR) rachète NetPlus Sàrl, fournisseur lausannois de services IT managés pour PME. GIR consolide sa position de leader régional des services de proximité en Suisse romande.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="8px" />
        <mj-text font-size="11px" padding="0px">
          <a href="https://example.com/gir-netplus" style="color: #6b7280; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db; padding-bottom: 1px;">Source ↗</a>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- ====== CTA ====== -->
    <mj-section padding="8px 40px 24px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-divider border-color="#D4952A" border-width="2px" padding="0 0 20px 0" />
        <mj-text font-size="16px" font-weight="700" color="#111827" line-height="24px" padding="0px">
          Un deal vous interpelle ?
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="6px" />
        <mj-text font-size="13px" color="#6b7280" line-height="20px" padding="0px">
          Contactez-nous pour une analyse détaillée ou un accompagnement sur une opportunité.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="14px" />
        <mj-button font-family="'DM Sans', Calibri, Arial, sans-serif" border-radius="6px" inner-padding="11px 28px" font-size="13px" font-weight="600" background-color="#D4952A" color="#ffffff" align="left" padding="0px" href="mailto:contact@auraia.com">
          Nous contacter
        </mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <!-- ====== FOOTER ====== -->
    <mj-section padding="16px 40px 28px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-divider border-color="#e2e8f0" border-width="1px" padding="0 0 16px 0" />
        <mj-text align="center" font-size="11px" color="#94a3b8" padding="0px" line-height="18px">
          Ce digest est préparé à partir de sources publiques.<br/>Les informations ne constituent pas un conseil en investissement.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="8px" />
        <mj-text align="center" font-size="10px" color="#94a3b8" padding="0px">
          Généré le 9 avril 2026 · Auraïa Capital Advisory
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

  </mj-body>
</mjml>
